data.chText: （尤指气得或惊讶得）说不出话的
data.enText: not able to speak, especially because you are extremely angry or surprised

means: (尤指气得或惊讶得)说不出话的

value.def: If you are speechless, you are temporarily unable to speak, usually because something has shocked you.

example.ex: Alex was almost speechless with rage and despair.
example.tran: 亚历克斯又生气又绝望，几乎说不出话来。
